      '<p>Everything is for rent! You can not think of something crazy that you cannot rent. Our customers vary from a bike rental company to a construction rental company with 200 locations nationwide! </p>\n\n<p>Huren.nl is a young and fast growing company. It is our mission to make the rental market open and transparent, so that our renters can easily and quickly find the right rental company. We have huge ambitions! Which cross national borders. In our wildest dreams the whole world ultimately rents through our platform!</p>\n\n<p>A lot of work is being done within the team. And if we are successful, we will celebrate that well, with a solid game of table football, table tennis or another cool activity. Every day we have lunch together and every Friday we close the week with a small drink.</p>\n\n<p>We deliver quality to our customers and always add value. For example, by increasing their online visiblity, or by helping them to optimize their rental website and increasing the return on their rentals. We are going for the long term and building an ambassador relationship. \'Hit and run\' is not our style. We are honest and transparent. Within the team, but also our customers can expect that from us.</p>\n\n<p>We are now looking for extra IT power: a PHP developer who, together with Stephan, Daan, Tijn and Eric, creates an optimal user experience on our website and improves our business processes. </p>\n\n<p><b>Your tasks:</b></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Design and implement cool technologies to optimize user experience;</li>\n<li>Improve the look and feel of the website;</li>\n<li>Maintaining and developing our databases and external links;</li>\n<li>Crunch big data and make cool dashboards;</li>\n<li>Solve IT problems (bugs);</li>\n<li>Working with and reporting in Jira.</li>\n</ul><p><b>What do we ask from you?</b></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>3 to 6 years of relevant work experience;</li>\n<li>Experience with PHP, MySQL and Nginx;</li>\n<li>Experience with HTML, CSS and JavaScript;</li>\n<li>Symfony, Linux and Salesforce knowledge is an advantage;</li>\n<li>Familiar with user interfaces and UX;</li>\n<li>Technical wonder that makes users happy;</li>\n<li>Talent for Tech lead.</li>\n</ul><p><b>What can we offer?</b><br>\nA young, fast-growing organization with an open and transparent working atmosphere, with satisfied customers and good future prospects. You get all the possibilities and freedom to develop our website and to create your own IT team. You can leave a big mark on the success and growth of Huren.nl. Of course we offer you a fixed salary in line with the market, preferably for a full-time position. Come and have a coffee to meet us. </p>\n\n<p><b>Interested</b><br>\nYou can apply via <a href=\'https://huren.heeft-vacatures.nl/php_developer_lead_tech_utrecht/217875/V819/solliciteren\'>this link</a>.</p>',
