      'Cracow',
      'Full Time',
      '<p>We are a Swedish SaaS company, simplifying the invoice automation process for mid-sized to large companies. Financial departments of the companies see great savings (money and time) using MediusFlow to process thousands of invoices per day.</p>\n\n<p>We\u2019re already an invoice automation market leader in Sweden \u2013 but the whole world awaits! Right now we\'re signing new deals in EU and US, and we still want to grow further. At the heart of the company is our Krak\u00f3w R&amp;D office where currently we are looking for a\u2026</p>\n\n<p><strong>DevOps Engineer</strong></p>\n\n<p>\u2026to strengthen our Cloud Operations team!\n You will be part of an ambitious team working hard to deliver a best-in-class cloud experience for our customers.</p>\n\n<p><strong>What will you do?</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li><p>Make sure MediusFlow cloud environments work great for our customers</p></li>\n<li><p>Find and implement improvements in our Microsoft Azure infrastructure</p></li>\n<li><p>Participate in design and development of Medius\u2019 CI / CD pipelines</p></li>\n<li><p>Deploy of new software releases in the production environment</p></li>\n<li><p>Write Powershell scripts that automate almost everything we do</p></li>\n<li><p>Monitor, measure and troubleshoot all aspects of our application and infrastructure</p></li>\n</ul><p><strong>Who will love it?</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li><p>You are a curious person who is eager to discover and implement new cloud technologies</p></li>\n<li><p>You enjoy getting things done and see the results of your work in production</p></li>\n<li><p>You think code and automation is much better than repetitive work</p></li>\n<li><p>You want to join a team of genuinely nice people that really care about their work</p></li>\n</ul><p><strong>What kind of experience should you have?</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li><p>We do a lot of scripting (we use Powershell). You should be able to write code to solve problems (in some language).</p></li>\n<li><p>CI / CD tools are important to us (we use Jenkins a lot). Experience in this area is useful</p></li>\n<li><p>Monitoring is also a big part of what we do (Graphite / Grafana). Experience in this area is relevant</p></li>\n<li><p>We use both Windows and Linux, you should be comfortable and willing to work with both\u2026but most of all we value a proven record of curiosity and drive!</p></li>\n</ul><p><strong>What we are offering?</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li><p>International environment with Swedish working culture</p></li>\n<li><p>Competitive salary, full time contract</p></li>\n<li><p>Essential software and equipment</p></li>\n<li><p>Flexible working hours, home office if needed</p></li>\n<li><p>Multisport card, private healthcare, life insurance</p></li>\n<li><p>Spacious office with stunning view over Krakow (no open spaces)</p></li>\n<li><p>In-house technical trainings, board games parties, occasional events, team breakfasts, games room, Fresh fruits, great coffee and Swedish Fika</p></li>\n</ul>',
